<p class="">What is the hon. Gentleman's definition of a reasonable man: is it one who agrees with him?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b56e6667-0c51-4890-a38e-898019bf04d4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
