               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-05-21/debates/2480a09d-17d2-4c84-adcd-b71354bdf406/Transport(GovernmentPolicy)#contribution-27973a8c-f8bf-44e0-b45e-80f5f55cee8b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">In that case, what does the hon. Member understand by the White Paper proposal for the liberalisation of licensing provisions? If that is not in the White Paper to allow more people to get on to the road, what does it mean?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-27973a8c-f8bf-44e0-b45e-80f5f55cee8b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
