<p class="">In fairness, I gave way constantly.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-84cee7e9-56c8-4265-b98c-4ee7c10ef3f4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
