                Mr. G. Lindgren  (Wellingborough)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9db37b72-b4ed-4c2f-9635-0ae09f14e7ae" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
