        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Take them back and have a go at it.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b8b77d20-4761-4e38-b4f0-6550939a4ca5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
