                Mr. Percy Shurmer  (Birmingham, Sparkbrook)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9503febc-b715-4b7e-ba51-c0118a2c976a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
