                Mr. Braithwaite
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-24dc82ba-d18c-40bf-ab5a-abe3cfe766a7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
